t Point, PA.[6] Good CB, McDermott L "Diet and serum potassium in patients on ACE inhibitors." JAMA 274 (1995): 538[7] "Product Information. Afinitor (everolimus)." Novartis Pharmaceuticals, East Hanover, NJ.', 1767365206);
