lled trial of ibuprofen compared with acetaminophen." Ann Intern Med 107 (1987): 628-35[2] "Multum Information Services, Inc. Expert Review Panel"[3] "Product Information. Toradol (ketorolac)." Roche Laboratories, Nutley, NJ.[4] "Product Information. Celebrex (celecoxib)." Searle, Chicago, IL.[5] "Product Information. Diovan (valsartan)." Novartis Pharmaceuticals, East Hanover, NJ.[6] "Product Information. Cozaar (losartan)." Merck & Co, Inc, West Point, PA.', 1767365206);
